entries.femaleVariant: Heard they're gonna cut our pay again.
Well, it's no wonder. You work less, you make less.
Just be happy they don't fire us. It were me, I'd toss all us seniors out with the trash.
Yeah, shoulda taken out a loan, got us some better muscle weaves while we could.
Gear like that, could sweat blood in the factory till you hit a solid seventy.
